Orphaned case refers to a problem where that case is not associated with a switch statement, making it orphaned. This can happen because of a misplace of a bracket or you forgot to make a break somewhere. Post a few lines of code before and after the error, then I’ll try to help my best. May not be able to, as orphaned cases are sometimes hard to solve. Also, tell us what you were trying to do when this error occurred.
